Top Undereye Finds Part 1 ✨

Under eye care is a constant journey and on this journey I've found very few products that have shown results on dark circles.

This Under Eye Brightening Oil from @thetribeconcepts is one such find!

Everything they make feels so pure and just with the fragrance of this one, you can smell the sandalwood.

It has Red sandalwood, Amla, star anise, Sweet almond oil and vitamin E.. all of these are super effective against dark circles.

Always remember, to see results on dark circles with topical products, it is advised to improve the lifestyle and habits causing these dark circles as well. 😌🫶🏻
